  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Land of Emag is in trouble!</strong> Experience a new 2D retro dungeon crawler in a way like never before!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c5b130f483d3f361bc2c08aee1652f7a.poster.avif?t=1672994143\" width=562 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c5b130f483d3f361bc2c08aee1652f7a.webm?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c5b130f483d3f361bc2c08aee1652f7a.mp4?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Are you up to the challenge Hero?</i></strong><br><strong>Choose</strong> your hero wisely, between an Egg(<i>Yes an egg...</i>), a mighty swordfighter, or an old... yet powerful wizard!<br><strong>Traverse</strong> through 10 unique dungeons and slay the 7 mighty beasts.<br><strong>Battle</strong> countless monsters, and foes in an all new real time battle system.<br><strong>Collect</strong> the Shori Stones, and unlock elemental powers to use in battle and in the overworld.<br><strong>Discover</strong> all the hidden secrets throughout the land.<br><strong>Defeat</strong> Purdrag and rid the land of Emag from the wrath of evil!<br>Victory is in your hands! Remain Victorious!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/1d89f8c4cb9a2158ab6b9ed0b0072f3e.poster.avif?t=1672994143\" width=568 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/1d89f8c4cb9a2158ab6b9ed0b0072f3e.webm?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/1d89f8c4cb9a2158ab6b9ed0b0072f3e.mp4?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/22d474e457c52448c5287d0cc3be627c.poster.avif?t=1672994143\" width=378 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/22d474e457c52448c5287d0cc3be627c.webm?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/22d474e457c52448c5287d0cc3be627c.mp4?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/dda20e3af3f0924ee7f8d5f8026f0fea.poster.avif?t=1672994143\" width=556 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/dda20e3af3f0924ee7f8d5f8026f0fea.webm?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/dda20e3af3f0924ee7f8d5f8026f0fea.mp4?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c61e8424203ffbfb8f172d5d63d973f5.poster.avif?t=1672994143\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c61e8424203ffbfb8f172d5d63d973f5.webm?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000560/extras/c61e8424203ffbfb8f172d5d63d973f5.mp4?t=1672994143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
